Summary: Scroll optimisations for Windows
Class: wish
Difficulty: tricky
Priority: medium
Content-type: text/x-html-body

<p>
Think about pre-building a bitmap for better scrolling, or
possibly just doing the old scroll optimisations over again and
getting them right.

<p>
Quite apart from the performance improvement, this may also improve
the experience of people using screen reader software such as JAWS.
